import { Box, Flex, Text} from "@chakra-ui/react";
import { Image } from "@chakra-ui/image";

import GoBlochainImg from "./";

export function Footer() {
  return (
    <Box
      width="100%"
      borderTop="1.5px solid #E2E2E2"
      p="25px"
      position="sticky"
      px="20px"
      as="footer"
      backgroundColor="#FFFFFF"
    >
      <Flex
        flexWrap="wrap"
        maxW="1367px"
        alignItems={{ sm: "flex-start" }}
        justifyContent="space-between"
      >
        <Text 
        fontFamily= "Roboto"
        fontStyle= "normal"
        fontWeight= "normal"
        fontSize= "14px"
        lineHeight= "16px"
        >
            Â© GoTokens. Todos os direitos reservados.
        </Text>
        <Flex>
            <Text
            fontFamily= "Roboto"
            fontStyle= "normal"
            fontWeight= "normal"
            fontSize= "14px"
            lineHeight= "16px"
            >
                Um produto feito com carinho pela  
           </Text>
           <Image src={GoBlochainImg}/>
        </Flex>
      </Flex>
    </Box>
  );
}
